Challenges with cost-utility analyses of behavioural interventions among older 
adults at risk for dementia.

Davis JC(1), Bryan S(2), Marra CA(3), Hsiung GY(4), Liu-Ambrose T(5).

Author information:
(1)Centre for Clinical Epidemiology and Evaluation, Vancouver Coastal Health 
Research Institute, Vancouver, Canada School of Population and Public Health, 
